### Acceptance criteria
- Given /waitlist page, when loaded, then shows branded signup form
- Given invalid email format, when typed, then inline error shown before submit
- Given valid email submitted, when loading, then button shows spinner
- Given API returns success, then show "Check your email" confirmation
- Given API returns error, then show error message with retry option
- Given /waitlist/verify?status=success, then show green confirmation
- Given /waitlist/verify?status=invalid, then show error with link back to /waitlist
- Mobile-responsive (looks good on 375px width)
- Uses shadcn/ui components (Input, Button)
- Build passes with no TypeScript errors

